3. Methodology
The engagement followed a standard penetration testing lifecycle:
```
Reconnaissance → Authentication Testing → Post-Auth Exploitation
→ Lateral Movement → Credential Harvesting → Privilege Escalation
```
Tools used: `nmap`, `curl`, `sqlite3` (strings), `sshpass`, `ssh`, `pykeepass`, standard Python 3.
